divs: Sighting Detailsi was out for a walk around the corner of my house and i saw a ufo right above telephone wires. it flew a straight path from behind me and then flew and dissapered past my site of the houses in front of me it went about 10 to 15 miles per hour and reminded me of the square ship on the opening credits of starwars. it made a buzzing sound and the craft seemed to have some sort of calming effect on me for some reason.
trends: There have been 4 other sightings in Hamilton Township

Summary: square ufo 20 feet above telephone wires going 15 miles per hour
